<BlogPost
  title="What Is a SANE Exam? Everything Survivors Need to Know"
  description="A Sexual Assault Nurse Examiner (SANE) exam can feel intimidating if you don't know what to expect. Here's a clear, compassionate breakdown of what it is, what happens, and what your rights are."
  date="February 15, 2026"
